set_metric_header(25.10)                              set_metric_header(25.10)

Name set_metric_header - Sets the name of a metric header
Syntax
Parameters  -id <db_id> Specifies the database ID. Data_type: string, optional
       -name <header> <_name > Specifies the name of  the  header.  Data_type:
       string,  required  -help Outputs a brief description that includes type
       and default information for each set_metric_header parameter. For a de-
       tailed description of the command and all of its  parameters,  use  the
       man  command:  man set_metric_header -value <header> <_value> Specifies
       the value of the header. Data_type: string, required
